&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Sports refer to physical activities that are competitive and organized, with rules and objectives. There are various types of sports that people can participate in, ranging from team sports to individual sports. Here are some categories of sports:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team sports: Team sports are those that require players to work together to achieve a common goal. Examples include football, basketball, soccer, volleyball, and hockey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Individual sports: Individual sports are those that are performed by a single person, with no team members involved. Examples include tennis, swimming, gymnastics, and track and field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Combat sports: Combat sports are those that involve physical contact between opponents, with the goal of defeating the opponent. Examples include boxing, wrestling, and martial arts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Water sports: Water sports are those that are performed in or on water, such as swimming, diving, water polo, and surfing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outdoor sports: Outdoor sports are those that are performed in natural environments, such as hiking, camping, rock climbing, and mountain biking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Winter sports: Winter sports are those that are performed on snow or ice, such as skiing, snowboarding, ice skating, and hockey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Extreme sports: Extreme sports are those that involve a high level of risk or danger, such as base jumping, skydiving, and bungee jumping.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sports provide numerous benefits, including physical fitness, social interaction, and stress relief. People of all ages and skill levels can participate in sports and enjoy the many benefits that they offer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

